name: EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessory
desc: An object that provides information about an unconfigured MFi Wireless Accessory Configuration accessory.

items.name: var manufacturer: String
items.desc: The name of the accessory's manufacturer.

items.name: var ssid: String
items.desc: The Wi-Fi SSID of the accessory.

items.name: var macAddress: String
items.desc: The primary MAC address of the accessory.

items.name: struct EAWiFiUnconfiguredAccessoryProperties
items.desc: Options that can be combined using the C bitwise OR operator to represent the properties of an unconfigured accessory.
